OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fvariable cloud and some long spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine, which may turn hazy at times
OL,8,Fwith high cloud. Mildest temperatures
OL,9,Facross northern coasts. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with clear
OL,12,Fspells. Turning cloudier overnight
OL,13,Fwith a few outbreaks of rain over the
OL,14,Fsouth, staying dry with some clear
OL,15,Fintervals in the north.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,18,Foutbreaks of rain. Becoming drier with
OL,19,Fsunny spells for a time in the
OL,20,Fafternoon, with northern parts
OL,21,Fgenerally the driest and brightest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
